==English==

===Etymology===
Borrowed from {{bor|en|fro|entretenir}}, from {{m|fro|entre||among}} + {{m|fro|tenir||to hold}}, from {{der|en|la|inter}} + {{m|la|teneō||hold, keep}}. For the noun, compare French {{m|fr|entretien}}.

